  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will evaluate a health services intervention to increase uptake of adolescent
      vaccines (HPV, Tdap, meningococcal conjugate, and influenza) among students enrolled in five
      school health centers by improving the consent process for parents.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
